| Release PrintPDF
| 8 Nov 2007

Set Release$Dir <Obey$Dir>.Release

| Update the application itself.

IfThere <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF Then Wipe <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF ~CFRV

Copy <Release$Dir>.^.!PrintPDF <Release$dir>.!PrintPDF ~CRV

| Update the external ReadMe file.

Remove <Release$Dir>.ReadMe

TextMerge <Release$Dir>.ReadMe <Release$Dir>.!PrintPDF.Resources.UK.HelpText <Release$Dir>.^.Manual.Header 5

| Update the Source folder.

IfThere <Release$Dir>.Source Then Wipe <Release$Dir>.Source ~CFRV

CDir <Release$Dir>.Source

Copy <Release$Dir>.^.c <Release$Dir>.Source.c ~CRV
Copy <Release$Dir>.^.h <Release$Dir>.Source.h ~CRV
Copy <Release$Dir>.^.Manual <Release$Dir>.Source.Manual ~CRV
Copy <Release$Dir>.^.Make <Release$Dir>.Source.Make ~CV

Unset Release$Dir
